<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Consegna Completata</title>
<style>
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 30px 20px; background: #f4f6f8; }
h2 { color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 15px; }
.back { display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #555; text-decoration: none; }
.back:hover { color: #000; }
.box {
    background: white;
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.07);
    max-width: 600px;
}
.msg-ok { background: #d4edda; color: #155724; padding: 14px; border-radius: 7px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: bold; max-width: 600px; font-size: 16px; }
table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 20px; }
th { text-align: left; padding: 9px 10px; background: #f0f0f0; color: #444; font-size: 14px; }
td { padding: 9px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 15px; }
tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.btn-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
a.btn {
    display: block;
    flex: 1;
    padding: 13px;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 7px;
    font-size: 15px;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
}
.btn-bolla     { background: #2980b9; }
.btn-bolla:hover { background: #1a6fa0; }
.btn-conteggio { background: #8e44ad; }
.btn-conteggio:hover { background: #6c3483; }
.btn-nuova { background: #27ae60; display: block; padding: 13px; color: white; border-radius: 7px; font-size: 15px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
.btn-nuova:hover { background: #1e8449; }
.nota { font-size: 13px; color: #777; margin-bottom: 15px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<a class="back" href="/">← Home</a>

<div class="msg-ok">✅ Consegna eseguita — magazzino aggiornato!</div>

<div class="box">
    <h2>{{ cliente }} — Riepilogo consegna</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>Prodotto</th><th>Quantità (bt)</th></tr>
        {% for prodotto, qty in richieste %}
        <tr>
            <td>{{ prodotto }}</td>
            <td><strong>{{ qty }}</strong></td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
    </table>

    <p class="nota">Scarica i documenti quante volte vuoi — il magazzino non verrà scalato di nuovo.</p>

    <div class="btn-row">
        <a class="btn btn-bolla" href="/download_bolla">📄 Scarica Bolla</a>
        <a class="btn btn-conteggio" href="/download_conteggio">🧮 Scarica Conteggio</a>
    </div>

    <a class="btn-nuova" href="/consegne">🚚 Nuova Consegna</a>
</div>

</body>
</html>
